sendMessages.label: Joñan mālim eo ej aikuj in jilkinḷọk juon ennaan .
sendMessages.tooltip: 0 meļeļein bwe aolep membōr ro remaron̄ jilkinļo̧k ennaan ko, im eļapļo̧k an ļapļo̧k oran eo meļeļein bwe eļapļo̧k mālim ko rej aikuj .

invite.label: joñan jerbal eo ej aikuj ñan karuwaineneik membōr ro rekāāl .
invite.tooltip: Set eo emaron̄ karuwaineneik membōr ro rekāāl n̄an ruum̧ eo .

kick.label: Kilkit joñan mālim eo ej aikuji .
kick.tooltip: Set eo emaroñ kōjepel ro ilo ruum̧ eo .

ban.label: Ear aikuj in bōbrae an ro uwaan .
ban.tooltip: Set eo emaroñ bōbrae ro ilo ruum̧ eo .

roomSettings.label: Ej kōṃṃan bwe en ḷapḷọk joñan an armej ro pād ilo ruum̧ eo .
roomSettings.tooltip: Set eo emaroñ kōṃṃan oktak ilo ruum̧ eo .

PermissionSettingsContent.description: joñan jerbal eo: 0-100, joñan an laplok oran eo ej aikuj
